description.secret: Trollcave is a vulnerable VM, in the tradition of Vulnhub and infosec wargames in general. You start with a virtual machine which you know nothing about â€“ no usernames, no passwords, just what you can see on the network. In this instance, you'll see a simple community blogging website with a bunch of users. From this initial point, you enumerate the machine's running services and general characteristics and devise ways to gain complete control over it by finding and exploiting vulnerabilities and misconfigurations.
description.note:
Doesn't work with VMware.
